      "start_time": 7880.0,
      "end_time": 9800.0,
      "text": "Rob: Welcome to 6 Minute English, the programme"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10800.0,
      "end_time": 11940.0,
      "text": "where we explore an interesting topic"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12240.0,
      "end_time": 15160.0,
      "text": "and bring you some useful items vocabulary. I'm Rob."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15320.0,
      "end_time": 16320.0,
      "text": "Neil: And I'm Neil."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16320.0,
      "end_time": 18880.0,
      "text": "Rob: Now Neil, I know you're a keen swimmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19600.0,
      "end_time": 21479.0,
      "text": "Neil: I am. I try to get to the pool once a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 21980.0,
      "end_time": 23220.0,
      "text": "and do a few lengths, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 23420.0,
      "end_time": 25400.0,
      "text": "Rob: That's good to hear because swimming"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 25400.0,
      "end_time": 27979.0,
      "text": "is one of the best sports for keeping fit."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 28200.0,
      "end_time": 31180.0,
      "text": "It's an aerobic exercise - aerobic means a very"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 31180.0,
      "end_time": 33540.0,
      "text": "active type of exercise that makes your"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 33680.0,
      "end_time": 35339.0,
      "text": "heart and lungs stronger."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35620.0,
      "end_time": 38459.0,
      "text": "The opposite of this is anaerobic - and for my question"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38580.0,
      "end_time": 41580.0,
      "text": "today Neil, I wonder if you know which of these activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 41580.0,
      "end_time": 43739.0,
      "text": "is an example of anaerobic"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43840.0,
      "end_time": 49160.0,
      "text": "exercise? a) weightlifting, b) kickboxing or c) dancing"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 49160.0,
      "end_time": 51120.0,
      "text": "Neil: I don't have a clue but I'll pick"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51300.0,
      "end_time": 53900.0,
      "text": "my favourite sport - a) weightlifting."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54360.0,
      "end_time": 57190.0,
      "text": "Rob: Is that really your favourite sport?!"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57240.0,
      "end_time": 59440.0,
      "text": "Anyway, we'll find out the answer at the end"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59600.0,
      "end_time": 60380.0,
      "text": "of the programme."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 60440.0,
      "end_time": 61480.0,
      "text": "Neil: So what about you Rob"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61560.0,
      "end_time": 63460.0,
      "text": "do you visit the swimming pool very often?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 63740.0,
      "end_time": 66840.0,
      "text": "Rob: Only to use the cafe! I don't like anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 66920.0,
      "end_time": 69280.0,
      "text": "aquatic - I mean connected to water."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 69560.0,
      "end_time": 72640.0,
      "text": "I just don't like getting wet - and swimming up and down"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72640.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "a pool is just boring!"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 74540.0,
      "end_time": 77200.0,
      "text": "Neil: Well there are alternatives to plain swimming."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 77200.0,
      "end_time": 79200.0,
      "text": "There's synchronised swimming..."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81980.0,
      "text": "Rob: Synchronised - that's moving together at the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81980.0,
      "end_time": 84800.0,
      "text": "time or speed as someone else."
