    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 88740.0,
      "end_time": 91220.0,
      "text": "Neil: How about the new craze of 'mermaiding'"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91220.0,
      "end_time": 93300.0,
      "text": "which is making a splash at the moment -"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93500.0,
      "end_time": 95300.0,
      "text": "in other words becoming very popular."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 95300.0,
      "end_time": 98320.0,
      "text": "The idea originated in America but is now popular in"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98420.0,
      "end_time": 99810.0,
      "text": "the UK and Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 100000.0,
      "end_time": 101120.0,
      "text": "Rob: OK. Tell me more!"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 101400.0,
      "end_time": 103500.0,
      "text": "Neil: Let's hear from an expert - Emma Longden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 103500.0,
      "end_time": 106440.0,
      "text": "who's founder of Fin2Fit - which runs classes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 106640.0,
      "end_time": 109520.0,
      "text": "teaching the skills of swimming safely like a mermaid..."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 110340.0,
      "end_time": 112680.0,
      "text": "Emma Longden: Mermaiding is putting a monofin on"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 112840.0,
      "end_time": 115840.0,
      "text": "your feet. Putting a beautiful tail on"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 115960.0,
      "end_time": 119360.0,
      "text": "and getting in the water and swimming like a mermaid."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 119880.0,
      "end_time": 122640.0,
      "text": "Rob: OK, so I would need to wear a monofin"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 122860.0,
      "end_time": 125740.0,
      "text": "- the prefix 'mono' means 'only one or single'"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126000.0,
      "end_time": 128919.0,
      "text": "- so a single fin -that's like a mermaid's tail"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 129380.0,
      "end_time": 131660.0,
      "text": "- then I just get in the water and swim around"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131740.0,
      "end_time": 134340.0,
      "text": "like a mermaid - I'm not so sure about that Neil"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 134480.0,
      "end_time": 136560.0,
      "text": "- I don't really know how mermaids swim!"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136740.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "Neil: There's more to it than that Rob."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 138320.0,
      "end_time": 140299.0,
      "text": "It's actually good for your fitness as"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 140300.0,
      "end_time": 141520.0,
      "text": "Emma can explain..."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 142200.0,
      "end_time": 145140.0,
      "text": "Emma Longden: It gives children's confidence in water"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145320.0,
      "end_time": 147660.0,
      "text": "a boost, it improves their water strength,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148400.0,
      "end_time": 150900.0,
      "text": "it gives you an entire body workout."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150900.0,
      "end_time": 153480.0,
      "text": "It works your cardiovascular system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 153700.0,
      "end_time": 157980.0,
      "text": "it works your legs, your core - it improves the children's"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 157980.0,
      "end_time": 161959.0,
      "text": "swimming technique, flexibility, balance, co-ordination"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 162820.0,
      "end_time": 165400.0,
      "text": "- you get the reward, you get the social aspect -"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 165580.0,
      "end_time": 167180.0,
      "text": "and alongside all of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 167180.0,
      "end_time": 169320.0,
      "text": "they're learning vital life skills along the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 169800.0,
      "end_time": 172440.0,
      "text": "Neil: So there are many benefits to mermaiding Rob."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172440.0,
      "end_time": 175600.0,
      "text": "Improving confidence, strength, technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 175320.0,
      "end_time": 178400.0,
      "text": "and it's good for your cardiovascular system"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 178300.0,
      "end_time": 180600.0,
      "text": "- cardiovascular relates to your heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 180860.0,
      "end_time": 181860.0,
      "text": "and blood vessels."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 182140.0,
      "end_time": 184540.0,
      "text": "Rob: I like the sound of the social aspect"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 184740.0,
      "end_time": 186720.0,
      "text": "- and by that Emma means being with other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 187600.0,
      "end_time": 190400.0,
      "text": "and having fun. It's an activity that's sociable."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 190860.0,
      "end_time": 193660.0,
      "text": "And it teaches life skills - useful skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 193840.0,
      "end_time": 196180.0,
      "text": "that help you deal with everyday challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 196480.0,
      "end_time": 199179.0,
      "text": "Well that's great for kids - and that's the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 199360.0,
      "end_time": 199940.0,
      "text": "Neil: What's that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 200120.0,
      "end_time": 203140.0,
      "text": "Rob: Mermaiding is for kids - so I can't get involved"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 203420.0,
      "end_time": 205540.0,
      "text": "- even if I wanted to... can I?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 205840.0,
      "end_time": 208620.0,
      "text": "Neil: You can Rob. According to Emma, it's growing"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 208620.0,
      "end_time": 210440.0,
      "text": "in popularity with adults too -"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 210580.0,
      "end_time": 213240.0,
      "text": "any excuse to live out your fantasies hey!"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 213760.0,
      "end_time": 216540.0,
      "text": "Emma Longden: There are so many adults that actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 216540.0,
      "end_time": 218799.0,
      "text": "kind of want to live out their childhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 218800.0,
      "end_time": 220640.0,
      "text": "dreams that they wanted to be a mermaid when they"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 220800.0,
      "end_time": 222580.0,
      "text": "were children and they didn't get the"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 222580.0,
      "end_time": 225520.0,
      "text": "opportunity and now it's here and now it's available..."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 225820.0,
      "end_time": 228280.0,
      "text": "So yes, we do a lot of adult classes as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231280.0,
      "text": "Neil: There you go Rob - living out your childhood"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 231460.0,
      "end_time": 234600.0,
      "text": "dreams - that doing things you wanted to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 234160.0,
      "end_time": 236320.0,
      "text": "when you were a child. Like being a mermaid!"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 236800.0,
      "end_time": 238940.0,
      "text": "Rob: Sorry Neil, that wasn't a dream for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 238940.0,
      "end_time": 241480.0,
      "text": "- although I did dream of swimming like a shark once!"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 241800.0,
      "end_time": 243540.0,
      "text": "Anyway, mermaiding is a good form"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 243780.0,
      "end_time": 246620.0,
      "text": "of aerobic exercise - but earlier I asked you"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 246680.0,
      "end_time": 249240.0,
      "text": "what an example of anaerobic exercise is."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 249440.0,
      "end_time": 254200.0,
      "text": "Is it... a) weightlifting, b) kickboxing or c) dancing"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256120.0,
      "text": "Neil: I said weightlifting. Was I right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 256140.0,
      "end_time": 258380.0,
      "text": "Rob: You were Neil, well done. Any exercise"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 258560.0,
      "end_time": 261360.0,
      "text": "that consists of short exertion, high-intensity movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 261579.0,
      "end_time": 264580.0,
      "text": "is an anaerobic exercise - such as weight lifting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 264580.0,
      "end_time": 267180.0,
      "text": "sprinting and jumping. I won't go into"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 267360.0,
      "end_time": 269820.0,
      "text": "scientific detail - but aerobics exercise"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 269820.0,
      "end_time": 272599.0,
      "text": "is done over a longer period of time and strengthens"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 272760.0,
      "end_time": 273940.0,
      "text": "the heart and lungs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 274000.0,
      "end_time": 277220.0,
      "text": "thereby improving the body's utilisation of oxygen."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 277480.0,
      "end_time": 278200.0,
      "text": "Neil: Thanks for that Rob."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 278200.0,
      "end_time": 280599.0,
      "text": "Now I think we should sprint through our recap"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 280760.0,
      "end_time": 282420.0,
      "text": "of some of the words we've talked about today -"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 282420.0,
      "end_time": 284820.0,
      "text": "starting with 'aerobic', which you just explained."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 285400.0,
      "end_time": 287940.0,
      "text": "\"Mermaiding is a good aerobic workout.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 287940.0,
      "end_time": 289960.0,
      "text": "Rob: Assuming you don't mind dressing up, of course!"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 290220.0,
      "end_time": 292960.0,
      "text": "Next we had 'aquatic' which refers to something"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 292980.0,
      "end_time": 295500.0,
      "text": "connected with water. \"Synchronised swimming"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 295500.0,
      "end_time": 297540.0,
      "text": "is an example of an aquatic sport.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 297740.0,
      "end_time": 299900.0,
      "text": "Neil: Ah, you slipped in another of our words there"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 299900.0,
      "end_time": 301900.0,
      "text": "- 'synchronised' - which means 'moving"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 302600.0,
      "end_time": 305400.0,
      "text": "together at the same time or speed as someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 305400.0,
      "end_time": 307720.0,
      "text": "or something else'. \"We synchronised our watches"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 307900.0,
      "end_time": 309919.0,
      "text": "so that we all arrived at the same time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 309920.0,
      "end_time": 311520.0,
      "text": "Rob: Good idea - you're always late Neil."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 312260.0,
      "end_time": 314420.0,
      "text": "Then we mentioned 'mono' which means 'one'"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 314580.0,
      "end_time": 317500.0,
      "text": "or 'single' and is used as a prefix on words such as"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 317680.0,
      "end_time": 320240.0,
      "text": "'monochrome' - one colour - or 'monorail'"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 320560.0,
      "end_time": 322280.0,
      "text": "- a train running on a single track."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 322600.0,
      "end_time": 324840.0,
      "text": "Neil: Then we heard the word 'cardiovascular'"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 324840.0,
      "end_time": 327200.0,
      "text": "- a word that relates to the effect on your"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 327240.0,
      "end_time": 330400.0,
      "text": "heart and lungs. \"Experts say those who quit"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 330400.0,
      "end_time": 332840.0,
      "text": "smoking could also quickly reduce their risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 332960.0,
      "end_time": 334659.0,
      "text": "of cardiovascular disease.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 334940.0,
      "end_time": 336860.0,
      "text": "Rob: Finally, we also mentioned 'social' -"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 337800.0,
      "end_time": 339560.0,
      "text": "this adjective relates to activities that you do"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 339700.0,
      "end_time": 341760.0,
      "text": "with other people and are usually fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 342600.0,
      "end_time": 344580.0,
      "text": "\"Now I live in London, I have a great social life.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 345800.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "Neil: Well you never invite me out Rob!"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 347780.0,
      "end_time": 350990.0,
      "text": "Anyway, that's it for this edition of 6 Minute English."
